    <item>
      <title>Version 0.3.0</title>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 08:44:25 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>0.3.0</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[Faster suggestions: fixed delays cut and stale generations restarted early — ghosts now appear in roughly a third of the time. Gibran now holds back suggestions the model itself is unsure about instead of showing weak ones. Suggestions always continue your own message — no more ghost replies when your draft contains a question. Mid-word suggestions complete the word and continue the phrase, and a typed-through ghost grows back into a full suggestion. Ignoring a ghost no longer silences similar suggestions for a day.]]></description>
